company.description:
ENVIRON is a leading international Environmental and Life Sciences consultancy. Our Product Compliance Services manage producer compliance with WEEE, Packaging, Batteries, REACH and RoHS legislation, including: assessment of company legal exposure to EU WEEE, Batteries and Packaging Regulations; a web-based solution to manage EU B2B WEEE compliance; and managing WEEE, Batteries and Packaging compliance scheme membership.&#13;
&#13;
- Managing supply chain substance declarations for REACH, RoHS, Batteries and Packaging compliance&#13;
&#13;
- Regular updates to EU WEEE, Batteries and Packaging law
